name: Richard Harbour
text: This is tim harbour. They screwed over my ole lady with a vape. We paid 50 dollars for a vape. And the one i seen in the store was new and never used. So i put it in my car and didnt open the box until i got home. And it wasnt the same one. It already had juice in it and dirty crud in the holes in it. So i carried it back and they refused to give us anything in return and told us to leave. . I suggest yall dont do business with very rude and unrespectable people. I f i could have gave them 0 stars i would have.

name: Emily Walker
text: Literally the one Stop store for everything. All the way from fine wine, to tanning beds! Fresh food cooked daily, super awesome workers, great line of CBD and vape equipment, just all around amazing!

resp.text: Awesome glad to have u as a loyal customer

name: Op Zorb
text: A nice store with everything you need. From good to house hold items. A great little liqueur store with fair prices. Friendly staff.

name: Penny Lightsey
text: That night shift lady is such a hard worker. Always helpful

name: Mariah Cassels
text: Great prices, good pizza & a good selection of food, household needs & great vape & juice prices!

name: Hina Patel
text: Best gas station with beer, wine, and liquor prices in town. Pizza is always fresh and free  additional toppings!!!

name: misty artis
text: Truely your one stop for all your needs . great pizzs and friendly staff

name: Tony Willy
text: Ever since that Misty girl took over as manager. One Stop has become the go to place, not just for the neighborhood, but for surrounding county's. 110% improvement way to go misty.
